Elbit Systems Awarded $25 Million Contract to Supply DIRCM Systems to an International Organization
Elbit Systems Awarded $25 Million Contract to Supply DIRCM Systems to an International Organization

May. 24, 2017 at 3:46 a.m. ET
on PR Newswire - PRF











Elbit Systems Ltd.


            
            Elbit Systems Ltd. is a technology company, which develops and supplies a portfolio of airborne, land and naval systems and products for defense, homeland security and commercial aviation applications. The company's systems and products are installed on new platforms, and also perform platform modernization programs. Its support services includes military aircraft and helicopter systems; helmet mounted systems; commercial aviation systems and aero-structures; unmanned aircraft systems and unmanned surface vessels; land vehicle systems; command, control, communication, computer and intelligence systems; electro-optic and countermeasures systems; homeland security systems; electronic warfare and signal intelligence systems; and various commercial activities. Elbit Systems was founded in 1996 and is headquartered in Haifa, Israel.

            
            (See Full Profile)


  




